title: Cancel 5% P3D fee for Ycrv Pool.
body: Y3D incentive for Ycrv pool(Pool1) is gonna stop on December 4th, thanks for the initial P3D offer, Y3D V2 and Unisave has successfully delivered. We could cancel p3d fee for pool1, so that the locked up liquidity can be migrate and join to Unisave.
